{"tid":2030781,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"違反中英聯合聲明，雙方還原基本步，根據南京條約，收返港島","createTime":"2020-05-23T04:00:49.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-23T12:55:07.000Z","uid":263648,"like":14,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"5eb2fe75fe74574c49957811eae1561a4e8492b2","tid":2030781,"uid":263648,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-23T04:00:49.000Z","msg":"根據中英聯同聲明，英國放棄咗永久擁有的港島，條件係50年不變、一國兩制。而家有一方違反合同，咁合同就要撤回，雙方還原基本步。呢個係警告佢地，後果自負。唔指望英國佬做野，但呢個POINT比美國佬無限放大都唔錯。<span style=\"color: red;\"></span><br />\n<br />\n南京條約:- <br />\n//因為大清戰爭失利，畀大英打到長江同京杭大運河交界嘅鎮江鷄毛鴨血，為咗保住呢條，就迫住簽條約。條約要大清賠錢、<strong><ins><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">割香港島畀大英</span></ins></strong>，以及准英人五口通商，同英人犯事由英方審，即係治外法權。//<br />\n<a href=\"https://zh-yue.wikipedia.org/wiki/%E5%8D%97%E4%BA%AC%E6%A2%9D%E7%B4%84\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fzh-yue.wikipedia.org%2Fwiki%2F%25E5%258D%2597%25E4%25BA%25AC%25E6%25A2%259D%25E7%25B4%2584&d=Ii3GHnPqKzd0SLaHQS96CEYnXQRGGZgEWtwyrMN1cgk%3D&h=e999de78\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://zh-yue.wikipedia.org/wiki/%E5%8D%97%E4%BA%AC%E6%A2%9D%E7%B4%84</a>"},{"pid":"2c937f0e9b1ba990f627a89ff2f6df2c7ea5e732","tid":2030781,"uid":11719,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-23T04:03:44.000Z","msg":"同中國佬講呢D野有用咩？"},{"pid":"df555b62c8b223e559fb3c7c30390e6479c8d575","tid":2030781,"uid":263648,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"2c937f0e9b1ba990f627a89ff2f6df2c7ea5e732","tid":2030781,"uid":11719,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-23T04:03:44.000Z","msg":"同中國佬講呢D野有用咩？"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-23T04:06:46.000Z","msg":"而家show hand緊，呢d咪chips囉"},{"pid":"f742316f738417a310f038b3c4009dc8b3e8213a","tid":2030781,"uid":331973,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-23T04:27:17.000Z","msg":"英國有道義行使，但佢會吾會執行同點執行，無人預計到，不過同無賴講合約，都係歷史文件"},{"pid":"ed90b44d5b762504173f9dc45cd6e21a21919cbd","tid":2030781,"uid":263648,"like":0,"dislike":0,"scor